intro: Collect energy, grow your tail, and fill the SPACE HOLE in this bite sized arcade game.
description:
SPACE HOLE is a bite sized arcade game where you grow a tail of energy and deposit it into the SPACE HOLE while avoiding enemies and obstacles. Dunking large amounts of energy into the SPACE HOLE will net you a point multiplier, but the more points you have will bring about more challenge -- so act fast!

This simple game expects no more than a minute or two of the player's time for a round. Try to beat your high score and complete all 10 achievements while enjoying a reactive music track from James Bennett.
